You are tasked with implementing a function that checks whether a given HTML string has properly matched opening and closing tags. In HTML, tags must be properly nested and closed in the correct order. For example, `<div><p></p></div>` is valid, while `<div><p></div></p>` is not.

You are given the following code snippet as a starting point for your implementation:

```rust
